accessibility.text: Red makes his way back to the old woman's home. She greets him with a sigh of relief and a hug. There's a knock on the door.
Red hides as the woman opens the door for the hunter and Dodger.
The woman tells the hunter that Red is off-limits. The hunter says if he ever sees the fox on his property again, he'll kill him.
The hunter goes back into his home with Dodger by his feet.
